Subject: [PATCH 41/64] mtk: luci-app-turboacc: refactor to support current
 framework - since we have adjusted hnat toggle and stats return formats,
 along with binding threshold setting way, we refactored hnat related settings
 and value parsing in rpc calls - we removed some deprecated flags that were
